name: Poster of the week: New York Cheesecake
description: Introducing our New York Cheesecake poster. It forms part of a series of five limited edition cake posters produced to celebrate a baking competition. The simplified graphic prints showcase a selection of baked classics including Tiramisu, Millionaire’s Shortbread, Battenberg and Cherry Bakewell. Details: – Limited edition – A1 – Digital print – 270gsm Colorplan For more imagery and details about the project, please visit our website here. Please note: price includes VAT and first class postage & packaging within the UK. Frame not included.
